@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dpbczr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(0.97)
    tmp = (v0 / ((v1 + 0.56 + v2 + 0.36) / (v1 + 0.24 + tmp + 0.63)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.sin(v0 + 0.98) * v2))
    v0 = (v0 + ((v2 + 0.03 / v2 + 0.71) * (v1 + 0.18 - v2 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
